# Template for `agps.properties`. Copy this file to `agps.properties`
# (gitignored sibling, same directory) and fill in your u-blox
# AssistNow developer token. See `docs/AGPS_TOKEN.md` for how to
# recover one from the official iGPSPORT APK.
#
# This file is the primary source for `BuildConfig.AGPS_TOKEN` —
# overrides the `LIGPSPORT_AGPS_TOKEN` env var when present. Leave
# the value empty (or delete `agps.properties` entirely) to fall
# back to `AgpsClient`'s runtime auto-fetch.
token=
